BC-CYBERSHRINK- AZR(a) 
 &HT;    THE SHRINK IS IN {ndash} ON THE WEB(a) 
 &HT;    (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)(a) 
 &HT;    By DOUG CARROLL(a) 
 &HT;    c.2000 The Arizona Republic(a) 
<TEXT>
<P>
   (PHOENIX) - You're struggling with a problem. You need to get
help, but you'd sooner be seen naked on the pitcher's mound at Bank
One Ballpark than in the waiting room of a psychiatrist's office.
</P>
<P>
   Perhaps there's no such stigma, but your budget leaves little
