<HEADLINE>
BEAUTY FLASH: CLEAN LIVING  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  ATTENTION EDITORS: The following material from The New York Times
Syndicate is for use by clients of ``HIGH STYLE AND MORE.''
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
For purchase information, see end of text. 
 &HT;    
 (Four color slides.) 
 From W magazine 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
 &HT;    
 SOAP STARS  
 &HT;    It has been in business since 1695, so it's pretty safe to say
that French soap and fragrance maker Roger &AMP; Gallet knows a lot
about the art of making soap.
 &HT;    Its newest products, Gardener's Special Soaps, come in such
flavors as Cherry Tomato, Lettuce and Carrot; they contain actual
vegetable extracts and smell good enough to bathe in. Available at
Henri Bendel, Nordstrom, Bloomingdale's and Marshall Fields.
 &HT;    
 MRS. FROSTY  
 &HT;    In the thick of summer, just the idea of wearing makeup can make
anyone break into a sweat. To the rescue: Aveda's new Cooling
Calming Cover Sheer Face Tint (a foundation) and Aveda Cooling
Calming Color Eye/Cheek Tint (a blush).
 &HT;    They not only keep you polished but also promise to lower body
temperature by five degrees _ thanks to formulas that contain
almost 50 percent water. And when the heat's on, this is definitely
a good thing. Aveda, (800) 283-3224.
 &HT;    
 WILD CARD  
 &HT;    With her first foray into makeup, Iman _ the Somalian
supermodel, mother-to-be and wife of David Bowie _ proved that she
knew how to do basic, wearable makeup. Now, with her creation of
I-Iman Makeup, she's showing the world her uninhibited side.
 &HT;    For this collection, Iman has unleashed a few tricks of her
trade, such as I-Matte, a gel spray that instantly seals makeup,
and I-Shimmer, an iridescent powder with glorious shine in a
rainbow of shades. Exclusively at Sephora.
 &HT;    
 CRYSTAL LIGHT  
 &HT;    When mineral makeup was first introduced a few years ago, it was
dismissed as a quirky trend.
 &HT;    Francie Willis, the owner of the Urban Retreat Day Spa in
Houston, is setting out to change that with Franche, her extensive
collection of water-resistant mineral makeup with freeze-dried
vitamins.
 &HT;    Particularly appealing is Lip Luscious, an iridescent gloss made
from plant-derived liquid crystals. Available at Henri Bendel and
at (877) 372-4243. c.2000 Fairchild Publications 
