<P>
   VEGGIE-SALADS _ Even when sources for fresh salad greens dry up,
there still are salads to be made from the local vegetable bounty.
Corn salad is an easy and favorite option once the first taste of
corn on the cob has been sated. Tomatoes and cucumbers partner in a
classic Greek chopped salad with olives and feta cheese. Summer
squash, green and yellow, make a colorful salad. (Dayton Daily
News). 20. WITH PHOTOS, RECIPES.
