<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-11 14:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9004 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u p BC-CAMPAIGN-TIPPER-BOS &LR;      07-11 0887
