<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-11 17:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9233 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u p BC-CAMPAIGN-GORE-BOS &LR;      07-11 0761
