season. Will the biggest of the portals make money? Wall Street has
been kicking its stock around lately pondering whether the web
advertising model it depends on makes sense. The analysts who study
this company say not to worry. Some of the smaller Web presences
may fail as dot-com advertising budgets shrink, but not Yahoo.
(Katz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 17.
