<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-11 19:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9280 &Cx1f; taf-z
u d BC-NY-DUCASSE-2TAKES-NYT     07-11 1076
