bellow into a cell phone.
</P>
<P>
   Pomerantz at Virgin, meanwhile, has faith that on-board cellular
calls will not become just one more annoyance in air travel.
``Hopefully, people won't be shouting on the phones,'' she said.
``You have to assume that your passengers are polite.'' &QL;
