<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-11 22:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9467 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r f BC-RATTLE-AND-HUM-LADN     07-11 0484
